Executive Vice President of Krogerny  (NYSE:KR), Schlotman J Michael, buys 2,000 shares worth $45,457
According to Krogerny 's most recent Form 4 filing with the SEC dated Jun 26 01:01 PM, company Executive Vice President, Schlotman J Michael disclosed buying 2,000 shares at a cost of $22.73. At the time of this transaction (Jun 26), this trade was worth $45,457 in total. As of Jun 26, Schlotman J Michael now owns 328,947 shares in total worth about $7,411,504.857. 
